Hey has co-written songs with Australian electronic music duo Empire of the Sun on their 2013 album Ice on the Dune and their 2016 album Two Vines.
Empire of the Sun member Nick Littlemore also released the album Every River Tells a Tale with Hey and bassist Tim Lefebvre in 2018 as part of The 2 Leaves Project.
